column5: This is my buddy Jeff with his nice hen brown from thursday this girl could fight....  cliff...
Ya gotta love the colors on those Browns! Beautiful fish!

very nice cliff.  I'll see ur thurs hen and raise u a fri buck.  One of the best browns i've seen in one of the worst weathers i fished.  It was like a brick of cheddar cheese.  NOtice the run off already before 10am
great pic shompz    that yours or buddys fish??
Nice fish guys, glad to see reports in December...  Mike
Love those colourful browns.  Very sweet catch  Congrats.
thanks for making me jealous... Nice fish though
Great lookin fish.  The resolution looks good!
those canon SRL cameras cost alot more but i love the pics they produce...
cool report & awsome looking brown,man they look so pretty...way to go,and in a snowstorm at that,,,,die-hard
it was just rain actually but man she came down
Nice brown. Man that is some heavy rain W2G guys    jordan
